stateDiagram-v2
    state "Draft (confidence: low)" as Draft
    state "Active (confidence: medium)" as ActiveMed
    state "Active (confidence: high)" as ActiveHigh
    state "Deprecated" as Deprecated
    
    [*] --> Draft
    Draft --> ActiveMed : First real engagement
    ActiveMed --> ActiveHigh : 3+ engagements with iterative feedback
    ActiveMed --> ActiveMed : Evolution protocol\nengage → observe → correct → codify → version bump
    ActiveHigh --> ActiveHigh : Evolution protocol\nengage → observe → correct → codify → version bump
    
    ActiveMed --> Deprecated : Superseded
    ActiveHigh --> Deprecated : Superseded
    Deprecated --> [*]
